name: What Comes Up Must Come...
description:
If you see anything weird, pretend as if you didn't see anything at all.  See no evil, hear no evil, do no evil.  Ignorance is bliss.

Music credited to Frederic Lardon from Freemusicarchive.org

Sound effects credited to freesound.org

Plugins credited to Sumrndmdde  http://sumrndm.site and Yanfly

(Reminder: this game is only part of the final product.

Also, V. 1.001 is just a very small update that just fixes a few glitches, but is separate just in case something goes bad.)
